11#ifndef API_AUDIO_CODECS_BUILTIN_AUDIO_ENCODER_FACTORY_H_

14#include "api/audio_codecs/audio_encoder_factory.h"
15#include "api/scoped_refptr.h"
16
17namespace webrtc {
18
19// Creates a new factory that can create the built-in types of audio encoders.
20// Note: This will link with all the code implementing those codecs, so if you
21// only need a subset of the codecs, consider using
22// CreateAudioEncoderFactory<...codecs listed here...>() or
23// CreateOpusAudioEncoderFactory() instead.
24rtc::scoped_refptr<AudioEncoderFactory> CreateBuiltinAudioEncoderFactory();
25
26} // namespace webrtc
